### Variables

@id = {{createCircuito.response.body.data.id}}


### GET ALL - Obtener todos los circuitos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos

### GET ONE - Obtener un circuito específico por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos/{{id}}

### POST - Crear un nuevo circuito
# @name createCircuito
POST http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Circuito de Mónaco",
  "country": "Mónaco",
  "length": 3.337,
  "year": 1929
}

### PUT - Actualizar un circuito completo
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Circuito de Mónaco",
  "country": "Mónaco",
  "length": 3.337,
  "year": 1929
}

### PATCH - Actualizar parcialmente un circuito
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "length": 3.340
}

### DELETE - Eliminar un circuito
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/circuitos/{{id}}

